	</p>

	<ul
		class="flex w-full flex-col items-center lg:my-4 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-around lg:gap-6"
	>
		<li class="">
			<a href="/">
				<ButtonNavigation> Inicio</ButtonNavigation>
			</a>
		</li>
		<li class="">
